{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm a visual artist,"},{"time":2000,"text":"and I'm also one of the co-founders of the Plastic Pollution Coalition."},{"time":5000,"text":"I've been working with plastic bags,"},{"time":8000,"text":"which I cut up and sew back together as my primary material for my artwork"},{"time":11000,"text":"for the last 20 years."},{"time":13000,"text":"I turn them into two and three-dimensional pieces"},{"time":16000,"text":"and sculptures and installations."},{"time":19000,"text":"Upon working with the plastic, after about the first eight years,"},{"time":22000,"text":"some of my work started to fissure"},{"time":24000,"text":"and break down into smaller little bits of plastic."},{"time":28000,"text":"And I thought, \"Great."},{"time":30000,"text":"It's ephemeral just like us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"Upon educating myself a little further about plastics,"},{"time":36000,"text":"I actually realized this was a bad thing."},{"time":39000,"text":"It's a bad thing that plastic breaks down into smaller little bits,"},{"time":42000,"text":"because it's always still plastic."},{"time":44000,"text":"And what we're finding"},{"time":46000,"text":"is that a lot of it is in the marine environment."},{"time":48000,"text":"I then, in the last few years,"},{"time":50000,"text":"learned about the Pacific garbage patch and the gyre."},{"time":53000,"text":"And my initial reaction --"},{"time":55000,"text":"and I think this is a lot of people's first reaction"},{"time":57000,"text":"to learning about it --"},{"time":59000,"text":"is, \"Oh my God!"},{"time":61000,"text":"We've got to go out there and clean this thing up.\""},{"time":63000,"text":"So I actually developed a proposal"},{"time":65000,"text":"to go out with a cargo ship"},{"time":67000,"text":"and two decommissioned fishing trawlers,"},{"time":69000,"text":"a crane, a chipping machine"},{"time":72000,"text":"and a cold-molding machine."},{"time":74000,"text":"And my intention was to go out to the gyre,"},{"time":76000,"text":"raise awareness about this issue"},{"time":78000,"text":"and begin to pick up the plastic,"},{"time":80000,"text":"chip it into little bits and cold mold it into bricks"},{"time":83000,"text":"that could potentially be used as building materials"},{"time":86000,"text":"in underdeveloped communities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"I began talking with people"},{"time":92000,"text":"who actually had been out to the gyre"},{"time":94000,"text":"and were studying the plastic problem in the marine environment"},{"time":97000,"text":"and upon doing so,"},{"time":100000,"text":"I realized actually that cleaning it up"},{"time":102000,"text":"would be a very small drop in the bucket"},{"time":105000,"text":"relative to how much is being generated"},{"time":107000,"text":"every day around the world,"},{"time":110000,"text":"and that actually I needed to back up and look at the bigger picture."},{"time":112000,"text":"And the bigger picture is:"},{"time":114000,"text":"we need to find a way to turn off the faucet."},{"time":117000,"text":"We need to cut the spigot"},{"time":119000,"text":"of single-use and disposable plastics,"},{"time":121000,"text":"which are entering the marine environment every day"},{"time":124000,"text":"on a global scale."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"So in looking at that, I also realized that I was really angry."},{"time":129000,"text":"I wasn't just concerned about plastic"},{"time":132000,"text":"that you're trying to imagine out in the middle of the Pacific Ocean --"},{"time":134000,"text":"of which I have learned there are now"},{"time":136000,"text":"11 gyres, potentially, of plastic"},{"time":138000,"text":"in five major oceans in the world."},{"time":141000,"text":"It's not just that gyre of plastic that I'm concerned about --"},{"time":144000,"text":"it's the gyre of plastic in the supermarket."},{"time":146000,"text":"I'd go to the supermarket and all of my food is packaged in plastic."},{"time":149000,"text":"All of my beverages are packaged in plastic,"},{"time":151000,"text":"even at the health food market."},{"time":154000,"text":"I'm also concerned about the plastic in the refrigerator,"},{"time":157000,"text":"and I'm concerned about the plastic and the toxins that leach from plastic"},{"time":160000,"text":"into us and into our bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"So I came together with a group of other people"},{"time":165000,"text":"who were all looking at this issue,"},{"time":167000,"text":"and we created the Plastic Pollution Coalition."},{"time":170000,"text":"We have many initiatives that we're working on,"},{"time":172000,"text":"but some of them are very basic."},{"time":174000,"text":"One is: if 80 to 90 percent"},{"time":177000,"text":"of what we're finding in the ocean --"},{"time":179000,"text":"of the marine debris that we're finding in the ocean -- is plastic,"},{"time":181000,"text":"then why don't we call it what it is."},{"time":184000,"text":"It's plastic pollution."},{"time":186000,"text":"Recycling -- everybody kind of ends their books"},{"time":189000,"text":"about being sustainable and greening with the idea of recycling."},{"time":192000,"text":"You put something in a bin and you don't have to think about it again."},{"time":195000,"text":"What is the reality of that?"},{"time":197000,"text":"In the United States, less than seven percent of our plastics are recycled."},{"time":200000,"text":"And if you really look into it,"},{"time":202000,"text":"particularly when it comes to plastic bottles,"},{"time":204000,"text":"most of it is only down-cycled,"},{"time":206000,"text":"or incinerated, or shipped to China."},{"time":209000,"text":"It is down-cycled and turned into lesser things,"},{"time":212000,"text":"while a glass bottle can be a glass bottle again"},{"time":215000,"text":"or can be used again --"},{"time":217000,"text":"a plastic bottle can never be a plastic bottle again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"So this is a big issue for us."},{"time":222000,"text":"Another thing that we're looking at and asking people to think about"},{"time":225000,"text":"is we've added a fourth R"},{"time":228000,"text":"onto the front"},{"time":230000,"text":"of the \"Reduce, Reuse, Recycle,\" three R's,"},{"time":232000,"text":"and that is refuse."},{"time":234000,"text":"Whenever possible, refuse single-use and disposable plastics."},{"time":237000,"text":"Alternatives exist;"},{"time":239000,"text":"some of them are very old-school."},{"time":241000,"text":"I myself am now collecting these cool Pyrex containers"},{"time":244000,"text":"and using those instead of Glad and Tupperware containers"},{"time":246000,"text":"to store food in."},{"time":248000,"text":"And I know that I am doing a service"},{"time":250000,"text":"to myself and my family."},{"time":252000,"text":"It's very easy to pick up a stainless-steel bottle"},{"time":254000,"text":"or a glass bottle,"},{"time":256000,"text":"if you're traveling and you've forgotten to bring your stainless-steel bottle"},{"time":258000,"text":"and fill that up with water or filtered water,"},{"time":261000,"text":"versus purchasing plastic bottled water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"I guess what I want to say to everybody here --"},{"time":266000,"text":"and I know that you guys know a lot about this issue --"},{"time":269000,"text":"is that this is a huge problem in the oceans,"},{"time":271000,"text":"but this is a problem that we've created as consumers"},{"time":274000,"text":"and we can solve."},{"time":276000,"text":"We can solve this by raising awareness of the issue"},{"time":279000,"text":"and teaching people to choose alternatives."},{"time":282000,"text":"So whenever possible, to choose alternatives"},{"time":284000,"text":"to single-use plastics."},{"time":286000,"text":"We can cut the stem -- tide the stem of this"},{"time":288000,"text":"into our oceans"},{"time":290000,"text":"and in doing so,"},{"time":292000,"text":"save our oceans, save our planet, save ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295000,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}